                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman L R</hi> 13). I took Bradley into custody, and found 16<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 2<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. on him—I had seen the prisoners in the London Road previously, about 200 yards from the shop.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Bedmore's Defence.</hi> Bradley stopped at the boot shop to buy a pair of boots; he tried on a pair, and Bilby pulled down a pair of shoes from a nail, and said "Try these on." I did not have the shoes at all, and did not go in with the intention of stealing them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Bilby's Defence.</hi> I took the pair of boots from the nail as he was trying one pair on. I did not notice they were women's boots. I had no intention of stealing them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Bradley's Defence.</hi> I went in to buy a pair of boots.</p>
